+ * primitive, not two, and no 32-bit time_t legacy. The op arg (FUTEX_WAIT
+ * vs FUTEX_WAIT|FUTEX_PRIVATE) is discarded — torpor is structurally
+ * per-Proc and the v1.0 process-shared futex isn't implemented anyway.
+ */
